rs et accessibles, afin de permettre aux francophones du Québec de mieux apprivoiser cette grande langue qui leur appartient et qu'ils partagent avec des millions d'autres à travers le monde.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn French.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Jun 2024) 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / Linguistics / General.2bisacsh1 aCastonguay, Charles, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLaforest, Marty, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLavoie, Thomas, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMercier, Louis, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPoisson, Esther, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aVerreault, Claude, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aWalter, Henriette, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Complete eBook-Package Pre-2010z978311127416408iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Upgrade eBook-Package pre 2010z978311127724040uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978276371347240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9782763713472423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9782763713472/original  a978-3-11-127416-4  ACUP Complete eBook-Package Pre-2010b2010  a978-3-11-127724-0  ACUP Upgrade eBook-Package pre 2010b2010  aGBV-deGruyter-alles